						- Jamming and percolation phenomena in restricted-valence systems (Phys. Rev. Research).
						- Phase transitions in associating lattice gases, revealing critical behaviors analogous to liquid-liquid equilibria (Phys. Rev. E).
						- Water-like anomalies in confined systems and mixtures, providing insights into thermodynamic and structural 
