					at BEES, I lead data platform initiatives including a secure Databricks Delta-sharing solution for 
					partner collaboration and an innovative automation framework integrating Jira with Terraform for 
					infrastructure management. Beyond technical projects, I mentor team members and contribute to technical 
					hiring, fostering team growth while maintaining hands-on involvement in system architecture and 
					implementation.

